Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糾正人類 奪回母親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的使命...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神會在這次戰爭中利用你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果戰鬥了 你的孩子也會死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不許欺負貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一點也沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還願再陪我跳舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫大忙了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到聖女大人跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不是聖女了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗塔總在我陷入危機時趕到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去 我們與人類的關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 巴哈姆特引發災難時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們同心協力 付出了巨大犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終保住了這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而人類失去了信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣稱不再需要神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後襲擊了我們的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至犯下了弒神之舉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他們意識到自身的過錯之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我們只能默默忍受此等暴行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不是決不能繼續容忍人類的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓侮辱諸神的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好見識一下我們的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為遇害的同胞雪恥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回世界的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百列大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾的力量還是未知數
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知能否承受這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾能封印人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經證明過很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空艇隊 上 上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵準備好投石車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把兵力集中到正面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊布置巨神兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利歐斯去死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王宮兵全去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要打仗就去外面打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了 再不逃就要開打了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰爭將考驗我們的真正價值啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與神戰鬥 你就沒任何感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？那又如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 別跟凱撒團長說一樣的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣戰的可是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後勤麻煩你們囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才是前線的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類就在安全地方看戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你們的王決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那態度是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亞思 去幹掉他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火開火開火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這拖著她們 你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑得很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再繼續走 妮娜就找不到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗塔 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來得是時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西繼續跑下去能到哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你瞎跳什麼舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還願再陪我跳舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 都抓穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我倒是沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為要掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們在那幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在給我鼓勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護好陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂...神是不是太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個光芒能封印人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑兵部隊在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對付這種對手不是他們的拿手好戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連他們也受不了那光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報告 城門被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就要殺入城中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個還未完成開發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在使用 不知陛下會出什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒徵求你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們也差不多該動身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒 把假手摘下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘下來之後固定在鎖上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先是伸出拇指 然後是中指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還用問？當然是要逃出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著彎曲拇指 伸出食指和小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 儘可能離它遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（咒語）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你做個更好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能用倒在那裡的傢伙的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這邊的門也打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你別把我另一隻假手也炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不是我 是麗塔設置的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說什麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都爆炸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微變得女人點了嗎 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德大人 平安無事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒 你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個 別磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:19:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你有鍛鍊自己的本事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是鍛鍊得槓槓的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招 看招看招
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神擊的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告別武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射擊之類的...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅 別在意
